data.title: BEST 1933 display NEWSPAPER EXTRA President CALVIN COOLIDGE DEAD Northampton MA
data.meta_description: Coolidge died suddenly from coronary thrombosis at "The Beeches," at 12:45 p.m., January 5, 1933. BEST 1933 display NEWSPAPER "EXTRA" edition - DEATH of Ex-President CALVIN COOLIDGE in Northampton MASSACHUSETTS.
